Subject: [PATCH] Remove unused #include <media/dvb_math.h>

m88rs6060.c includes <media/dvb_math.h> but doesn't use anything from
it (no calls to intlog2(), intlog10(), etc.). The header was removed
from the mainline kernel some time ago, so out-of-tree builds against
modern kernels fail with:

    fatal error: media/dvb_math.h: No such file or directory

Drop the include. The driver is unaffected — the include was a stale
leftover from earlier code.

Affects 1 file: m88rs6060.c.
---
diff --git a/drivers/media/dvb-frontends/m88rs6060.c b/drivers/media/dvb-frontends/m88rs6060.c
index 4525f75..f23ae87 100644
--- a/drivers/media/dvb-frontends/m88rs6060.c
+++ b/drivers/media/dvb-frontends/m88rs6060.c
@@ -5,7 +5,6 @@
  * Copyright (c) 2021 Davin zhang <Davin@tbsdtv.com> www.Turbosight.com
  *
 */
-#include <media/dvb_math.h>
 
 #include "m88rs6060_priv.h"
 #include <linux/mutex.h>
